  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Advocacy for Government&#x2019;s intervention towards achieving Certification and Accreditation of PWDs in</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project activities will cover:
- Baseline and End line Evaluation 
- Production of jingles
- 16 radio shows 
- Town Hall Meetings
- Production and dissemination of the PWD Act
- Lobby relevant stakeholders for the approval of nominees to the medical board and screening tool
- Work with strategic partners to develop a realistic proposal for the rolling-out key activities towards the certification process.
- SLUDI establishes a monitoring framework to monitor roll out of certification process</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To enable SLUDI deepen its engagements and lobbying with relevant partners including but not limited to ministries, departments and agencies for the certification of PWDs to be prioritised.</narrative>
  </description>
